    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for me, whether I\u2019m just heading to the store or taking a longer road trip. It runs beautifully and the interior is still really comfy and clean. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
