    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and a recently inspected rear subframe. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent service includes a VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment, ensuring optimal timing and compression. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this example offers a visceral, analog driving experience with precise turn-in and excellent lateral grip.",
