    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for driver. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a high-gloss luster; while there are minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing, the body panels are straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean. The premium upholstery shows only light bolstering wear on the driver's seat, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All interior electronics, from the heated seats to the premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and brake pad replacement just 1,500 miles ago. The engine idles quietly, shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. It comes with a clean title, two sets of keys, and a thick folder of maintenance receipts. This is an honest, dependable vehicle that looks great and performs even better.",
